\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5120987 AR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14769093\charrsid355495 Oh y}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2365796\charrsid355495 es. Piano, a mandolin and banjo}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14769093\charrsid355495 s, and guitars, yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12868611 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14769093\charrsid355495 Did you all sing as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5120987 AR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14769093\charrsid355495 No. There's never singing very much. They'd got no voices.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12868611 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14769093\charrsid355495 Did you all play together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5120987 AR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14769093\charrsid355495 Oh yes. We used to have Sunday n
ights you know, sitting round in here with a table and - then somebody'd go in the front room and play the piano for us you know, and we'd - have a musical evening. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12868611 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14769093\charrsid355495 Did your parents play games with you?
