Well, he a bit prejudiced against that because years ago - they used to - slow poison people if they got them well insured didn't they. Yes. Especially children. Oh yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12868611 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14769093\charrsid355495 How about sickness, for doctors bills and things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5120987 AR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14769093\charrsid355495 Well - father always paid them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12868611 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14769093\charrsid355495 But he didn't save up in a club or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5120987 AR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14769093\charrsid355495 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12868611 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14769093\charrsid355495 When you were still at school how did you get on with your brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5120987 AR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14769093\charrsid355495 All right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12868611 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14769093\charrsid355495 You didn't quarrel with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5120987 AR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14769093\charrsid355495 No. Well if we quarrelled, you know - one'd be pushed one way and one'd be pushed the other. Yes.
