\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5120987 AR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14769093\charrsid355495 Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12868611 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14769093\charrsid355495 In the yard at all, in your garden?
